# ━━━ Saturn Environment Variables ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this to .env and fill in your values

# ── Anthropic (Claude Opus) ──
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ── GitHub ──
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...
GITHUB_DEFAULT_REPO=Raviston6296/saturn

# ── Zoho Cliq ──
CLIQ_WEBHOOK_TOKEN=your-cliq-verification-token
CLIQ_BOT_API_URL=https://cliq.zoho.com/api/v2/channelsbyname/your-channel/message
CLIQ_AUTH_TOKEN=your-zoho-oauth-token

# ── Server ──
SERVER_HOST=0.0.0.0
SERVER_PORT=8000

# ── Agent ──
MAX_LOOP_ITERATIONS=20
THINKING_BUDGET_TOKENS=10000
WORKSPACE_BASE_DIR=/tmp/saturn-workspaces

